1471
01:42:08.540 --> 01:42:10.156
Okay.

1472
01:42:10.959 --> 01:42:12.870
Thank you.

1473
01:42:22.638 --> 01:42:23.878
Well, who did all of this?

1474
01:42:24.056 --> 01:42:28.050
