from my friends on the nursing staff.

1475
01:42:28.226 --> 01:42:29.716
Oh.

1476
01:42:43.283 --> 01:42:46.321
I've never seen anything so beautiful.

1477
01:42:46.953 --> 01:42:48.739
Neither have I.

1478
01:42:52.042 --> 01:42:53.532
Shall we?

1479
01:43:01.093 --> 01:43:03.425
